name: Tlaloc - Asc.1 & 2 - FGO
description:
This is a LoRA of Tlaloc Stage 1 and 2 Outfit from Fate Grand Order.

v3

Recommended Weight is 1.

for asc1 outfit = tlaloc,hair ornament,gloves,short hair,facial mark,headdress,feathers,cleavage,revealing clothes

for asc2 outift = tlaloc,long hair,hat,green beret,green jacket,off shoulder,longsleeves,black shorts,glasses,tinted eyewear

v2

Recommended Weight is 0.6 ~ 0.9. if it's too high the chances are that the glasses and eyes will be distorted when you try to remove the glasses. but, if it's too low sometimes the pants turn out to be long.
